pullRequest.body:
Add a few missing lemmas about the coercion `NNReal → Real`. Remove a bunch of `protected` on the existing coercion lemmas (so that it matches the convention for other coercions). Rename `NNReal.coe_eq` to `NNReal.coe_inj`

From LeanAPAP

Why do you drop the namespace here?

Also, the `mathlib3` name is still `coe_eq`.
```suggestion
#align nnreal.coe_eq NNReal.coe_inj
```
Should it be `_root_.GCongr.nnrealToReal_le_toReal`? I'm not sure.
Don't think it really matters at this point. We can wait a bit longer and make a mathlib-wide decision.
